{
  "stem": "1363.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was, as I said, the sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think that religious great uncle of the families have paid for him to stay there in that, and with false papers, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't recall that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I know he wasn't with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were only women, and the only male was that old father of my uncle who--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who spoke Russian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when I got into forced labor camp, that was in '44.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was 15.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was I 15 or 17?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was born in '27.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "17.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But a very shy-- a very timid and inexperienced 17, who didn't know anything about life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In a way, emotionally I was an adult, because I had to always lean on my own, myself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, my brother and I, were protecting each other sort of.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was no experiences in my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or, I didn't hear any, any teaching of worldly happenings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was somehow always-- because we didn't have the parents, and my uncle wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So most, probably the women, my auntie and my grandma, did not discuss certain things in front of us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I only know that when I went into this forced labor camp myself, we were digging grooves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How do you call that in English?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sort of like trenches?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trenches.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were preparing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew already by then that Russians are coming from one part of Hungary--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not far from Budapest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, not far.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can't recall where.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know we were taken, and I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was it a train?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was it a bus?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was it walking?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Again, a blank.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember standing at the trenches.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And coincidentally, one of my colleagues at work-- because by that time, I was 17.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
